summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 5.8°C), outside temperature (up 4.6°C), and inside temperature (up 2.5°C) and more moisture-laden rainfall (up 0.3 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 306 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 450 m), feels like temperature (down 3.1°C), and dew point temperature (down 3.1°C) when compared to today.
